
Competencies

4 basic functions of a persistent database Create Read Update Delete
Almost all applications with databases will have this functionality
REST (Representational State Transfer) is a standardized practice for HTTP syntax that optimizes scalability, performance, and modularity
REST pairs very well with CRUD functions
For web apps, RESTful routes are taken care of in the controller
In Sinatra, CRUD commands take the form of routes
Routes are declared in a clear and concise syntax   

Applications
Understand concepts of CRUD and write RESTful routes

http://www.restular.com/
